

Rollup
Rollup build commands:

es format
same as concatinate files
rollup SvgPath.js --format es --file bundle.js

iife format
closure with one "name" global accessor
rollup SvgPath.js --format es --name "SvgPathMod" --file iife_bundle.js




Browserify
To Build Original Require items with Browserify commands

give a global accessor of svgpath
browserify svgpath.js --standalone svgpath > browserify.concat.js

just bundle it
browserify svgpath.js -o browserify.bundle.js




